#Text=Wikinews Shorts : January 7 , 2009
#Text=A compilation of brief news reports for
#Text=Wednesday , January 7 , 2009
#Text=.
#Text=Strike on UN school in Gaza kills 40
#Text=Map of Gaza Strip .
#Text=Palestinian

#Text=medical officials report that a United Nations school in Gaza City , which was being used as a shelter for civilians , took a direct hit from an Israeli tank , killing more than 30 Palestinians on the 11th day of the assault .
#Text=Israeli officials have stated that rocket fire had emerged from within the school .

#Text=Doctors of the Kamal Adwan Hospital in Jabaliya report that an additional 10 people died at the hospital and they expect an increase in the casualties as more people may be on the way to the hospital .
#Text=Sources
#Text=" Strike on Gaza school ' kills 40 ' " — BBC News Online , January 6 , 2009
#Text=Mark Tran .
#Text=" Israeli shelling kills dozens at UN school in Gaza " — guardian.co.uk , January 6 , 2009
